{"tid":556151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★樓市暢旺，市民會較闊綽，年花價格貴一些都會買。？？？？","createTime":"2018-02-10T09:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T09:18:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1af81092d5207736e03bca8ab28941e771080aeb","tid":556151,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全港多個農曆年宵市場今日開始運作，其中最大型的維園年宵，有市民趁早上人流較少到場選購水仙和蘭花，亦特意選購花蕾較多的花，希望幾天後開花，剛好迎接新年。<br />\n<br />\n有主要售賣水仙的花檔檔主說，年花受寒冷天氣影響，普遍遲了開花。不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">她認為樓市暢旺，市民會較闊綽，年花價格貴一些都會買。</span><br />\n<br />\n亦有賣年花的檔主指，近日回暖，桃花及時盛開，今年年花零售價上升兩至三成，但估計銷情仍會較去年好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1380214-20180210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1380214-20180210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2ac68a03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1380214-20180210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cc9b8c75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1380214-20180210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"615d54402d6d675b8c46b3191f08a92f141d3107","tid":556151,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"d錢都擺晒落樓，何來消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa7262346c79dd4690a1c70691defcaafd66d99","tid":556151,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:06:28.000Z","msg":"d新屋咁細，有錢買都無地方擺<br />\n霍景良都唔洗出動就收皮"},{"pid":"c29a13e4653997510afbd54eaa00af044802c238","tid":556151,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa7262346c79dd4690a1c70691defcaafd66d99","tid":556151,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"20